    "Id": "185293",
    "ThreadId": "54842",
    "Html": "Yes, please if ther is a full list I could really use it.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nI just released a very sophisticated real-time app using the January 09 release of the datagrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nShould I upgrade to the March 09 release ASAP?&nbsp; One issue in particular that I see is scrollintoview sometimes bomb, and I think it is because I have deferred scrolling enabled and also a collection view getting updated on the UI thread by a background worker that the drids items source is bound to.&nbsp; I had to remove the automatic scroll to the top of the list functionality and it is woking ok for the time being.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks,<br>\r\nJon<br>\r\n<br>\r\n",
