    "Html": "Hi there.  Samantha Durante provided the following list to one of my team members.  This is for the March2009 release.<div>FYI</div><div>~Tracy<br><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"color:rgb(31, 73, 125);font-family:calibri;font-size:15px\">Here’s a high level list of the major bug fixes:</span><br></div><div><p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">&lt;o:p&gt; &lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0.05in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0.05in;margin-left:0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;vertical-align:middle\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:symbol;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">·</span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">        </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">DataGridColumn * width designer crash issue &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0.05in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0.05in;margin-left:0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;vertical-align:middle\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:symbol;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">·</span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">        </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">Un-clickable popups in DataGrid RowDetails &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0.05in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0.05in;margin-left:0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;vertical-align:middle\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:symbol;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">·</span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">        </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">DatePicker crash when setting IsEnabled to False &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0.05in;text-indent:-0.25in;vertical-align:middle\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:symbol;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">·</span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">        </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">DatePicker SelectedDate binding is not TwoWay by default &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">&lt;o:p&gt; &lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(31, 73, 125)\">At a more granular level, here is a list of the titles of thebugs fixed:  &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(31, 73, 125);font-family:calibri;font-size:15px\"><br></span></p><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=626 style=\"width:469.5pt;border-collapse:collapse\">    <tbody>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">Add Blend-specific DataGrid            design time icons (b/c our current ones show up with a pink background in            Blend)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid needs to provide            sorting info about the columns</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid - Popups in RowDetails            do not work correctly</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">Unhandled exception when a            DataGridTextColumn has * width and Window does not have fixed height and            width</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">Datagrid: Binding DateGridColumn            to Read-only data source generate exception in run-time</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid:            IndexOutOfRangeException thrown when row validation error occurs with            DataTable and trying to use the keyboard to navigate</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid: ArguementException thrown            when resizing a column initially set to SizeToCell and an empty ItemsSource</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid - Grouping disappears            when changing DataGrid.ItemsSource</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid performance is slow            when automation is active</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">Infinite relayout of DataGrid            when focus changes from row to details panel</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid Column header resizing            causes misaligned cells</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">NullReferenceException when a            DataGridRow does not have a DataGridOwner</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid Star Column Widths            incorrect when DataGrid was loaded with its Visibility not Visibile</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGrid - SecurityPermissions            Exception thrown in DataGrid.StartAutoScroll()</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DataGridComboBoxColumn doesnt            work properly with CollectionViewSource as its ItemsSource</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">Memory leak when binding            DataGrid to DependencyProperty</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">Decade Added or Substracted When            Highest Or Lowest Year Is Selected In A Decade View</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DatePicker breaks when            IsEnabled=false</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DatePicker Esc and Enter actions            not working</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">Calendar/DatePicker requires            explicit TwoWay Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;background-image:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-color:silver;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap;background-position:initial initial\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">DatePicker Icon is inverted when            FlowDirection is RightToLeft</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>        <tr style=\"height:15pt\">            <td valign=top style=\"width:350.35pt;border-top-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-left-style:none;border-width:initial;border-color:initial;border-bottom-style:solid;border-bottom-color:black;border-bottom-width:1pt;padding-top:0in;padding-right:5.4pt;padding-bottom:0in;padding-left:5.4pt;height:15pt;white-space:nowrap\">            <p><span style=\"color:black\">VisualStateBehaviorFactory.RegisterControlBehavior            can run into a NullReferenceException on a second thread</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:calibri, sans-serif;color:black\">&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;</span></p>            </td>        </tr>    </tbody></table></div></div>",
